117
00:07:15,520 --> 00:07:19,200
He's embarrassing Mrs. Wu.

118
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:25,840
Long live Your Majesty!

119
00:07:25,840 --> 00:07:27,560
Empress Dowager.

120
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:31,960
May you live long!

121
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:36,320
Greetings, Your Majesty.

122
00:07:36,320 --> 00:07:39,000
Greetings, Empress Dowager.

123
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,440
You two

124
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:41,880
