179
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:39,280
You don't need to know.

180
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:45,680
Why do you talk so much nonsense?

181
00:13:45,680 --> 00:13:46,680
It seems today,

182
00:13:46,680 --> 00:13:49,040
I can't escape from you.

183
00:13:49,040 --> 00:13:51,080
