191
00:14:13,680 --> 00:14:15,880
then what would I do?

192
00:14:17,040 --> 00:14:19,280
You have killed so many people.

193
00:14:19,280 --> 00:14:20,440
Their resentment

194
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:22,520
has long turned into
fierce ghosts surrounding you

195
00:14:22,520 --> 00:14:24,840
and accompanying you day and night.

196
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:26,360
Can't you see them?

197
00:14:26,360 --> 00:14:28,720
They are nothing,

198
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:33,520
