201
00:14:37,640 --> 00:14:39,720
Or I'll kill them again.

202
00:14:39,720 --> 00:14:42,000
Am I also someone who deserves to die?

203
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,320
The people you mentioned

204
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:44,560
all share common traits,

205
00:14:44,560 --> 00:14:46,920
and you think they deserve to die.

206
00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:48,320
In your eyes,

207
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:50,640
do I also deserve to die?

208
00:15:08,680 --> 00:15:10,360
Even if you ask so many questions,

209
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:12,880
you have to die anyway.

210
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:16,200
But…

211
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:20,760
I have to wait

212
00:15:20,760 --> 00:15:22,760
