213
00:15:23,280 --> 00:15:24,440
What are you waiting for?

214
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:27,920
I'm waiting for your blood to coagulate.

215
00:15:27,920 --> 00:15:29,520
Then when I take your heart out,

216
00:15:29,520 --> 00:15:32,080
you won't even bleed.

217
00:15:34,800 --> 00:15:37,400
I am Mrs. Shen.

218
00:15:37,400 --> 00:15:39,440
If you dare to kill me,

219
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:40,960
when they find you,

220
00:15:40,960 --> 00:15:43,960
they will certainly skin you.

221
00:15:45,680 --> 00:15:47,600
Even if I don't kill you,

222
00:15:47,600 --> 00:15:50,040
