I might

225
00:15:59,640 --> 00:16:02,400
kill you as well.

226
00:16:02,400 --> 00:16:04,440
I can plead for you.

227
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:06,720
He might leave you an intact body.

228
00:16:06,720 --> 00:16:09,640
We have a very good relationship.

229
00:16:09,640 --> 00:16:11,320
The whole Xiang'an City knows it well.

230
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:13,680
He will listen to me.

231
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:18,200
He will listen to me.

232
00:16:18,200 --> 00:16:19,800
He will listen to me.

233
00:16:19,800 --> 00:16:21,800
He will listen to me.

234
00:16:21,800 --> 00:16:24,000
Shut up!

235
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:25,560
You shut up!

236
00:16:25,560 --> 00:16:27,160
You shameless hussy!

237
00:16:27,160 --> 00:16:28,440
He won't listen to you.

238
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:31,680
He is mine, mine, mine!

239
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:39,496
Stop.

240
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:43,016
Let me go.

241
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:46,408
Liuniang.

242
