you've sprinkled flour on your clothes,

246
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:23,079
so the dog could follow your scent over here.

247
00:17:32,480 --> 00:17:35,368
How do you feel?

248
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:38,400
I-I'm fine.

249
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:40,920
But…

250
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:43,040
Have you caught the murderer?

251
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:05,120
But I had a dream.

252
00:18:05,840 --> 00:18:08,584
Jing Lin.

253
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:12,640
Take off her mask.

254
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:24,712
It's you.

255
00:18:32,200 --> 00:18:34,888
Liuniang.

256
00:18:37,200 --> 00:18:39,440
Take her into the Imperial Guards.

257
00:18:39,440 --> 00:18:40,680
Yes.

258
00:18:40,680 --> 00:18:41,760
Take her away.

259
00:18:41,760 --> 00:18:43,880
Yes.

260
00:19:05,400 --> 00:19:08,720
Liuniang, you're awake.

261
00:19:08,720 --> 00:19:13,480
